overview: Michelle Yee Sangster has over 18 years in the Internet and publishing spheres in the United States and overseas: She is an alumna of Yahoo and Overture where she managed business development and search and content monetization. Sangster was also a key player on the Junglee team and also spent time at Pointcast, WishClick, Cellectivity in the UK and Encyclopedia Brittanica. She is a graduate of UCLA and the Harvard Graduate School of Business .
